and cut out her heart.

01:22:00.420 --> 01:22:04.674
I guess she couldn't
predict the future for herself.

01:22:05.133 --> 01:22:07.510
The future isn't what it used to be.

01:22:07.969 --> 01:22:09.888
And your conclusions?
- I haven't any.

01:22:10.346 --> 01:22:13.892
All I know is that Johnny is running
around bumping off everyone he knew.

01:22:14.350 --> 01:22:17.562
And more and more,
