and it's scaring the shit out of me.

01:22:21.399 --> 01:22:25.487
So why don't you just level with me
and tell me what the fuck is going on?

01:22:26.404 --> 01:22:30.575
Just Johnny Favorite
and the debt that's owed to me.

01:22:31.034 --> 01:22:34.120
I have old-fashioned ideas,
about honour.

01:22:34.579 --> 01:22:37.415
