so he'll be okay there.

01:24:08.923 --> 01:24:13.845
You're welcome to stay here,
or I can get you a room.

01:24:14.304 --> 01:24:15.763
No, it's okay.

01:24:16.222 --> 01:24:19.476
I'm going to have a drink. Want one?

01:24:21.644 --> 01:24:23.688
Well, have one anyway.

01:24:27.609 --> 01:24:29.694
I've been thinking...

01:24:30.153 --> 01:24:34.491
What the hell did your mother see in
a guy like Johnny Favorite?

01:24:34.949 --> 01:24:38.828
I don't know. Whatever he had,
it sure stole her heart away.

01:24:39.829 --> 01:24:42.540
To tell you the truth,
the guy was a creep.

01:24:42.999 --> 01:24:45.335
She sure missed him.

01:24:45.960 --> 01:24:51.508
What does a lady see in a guy
who runs around chopping up pigeons?

01:24:51.966 --> 01:24:56.846
They say it's always the bad-asses
who make a girl's heart beat faster.

01:24:59.766 --> 01:25:01.935
Did she ever say anything about him?

01:25:04.813 --> 01:25:07.440
Just two things.
- What?

01:25:09.317 --> 01:25:14.447
