true evil as she ever wanted to come.

01:25:15.615 --> 01:25:16.950
What else?

01:25:17.784 --> 01:25:19.369
That he was a terrific lover.

01:25:24.833 --> 01:25:26.209
How old are you?

01:25:26.668 --> 01:25:29.045
