01:25:31.089 --> 01:25:32.966
Kind of young to have a kid, isn't it?

01:25:33.591 --> 01:25:35.718
Old enough.

01:25:37.387 --> 01:25:40.014
Where did the father go?
- I never knew him.

01:25:40.932 --> 01:25:42.267
I'm sorry.

01:25:44.060 --> 01:25:46.688
I don't know why I took this room.

01:25:47.814 --> 01:25:50.942
