01:30:56.915 --> 01:31:00.460
Somebody called Margaret Krusemark
figure in your missing persons case?

01:31:01.836 --> 01:31:05.423
No, why? - She's dead.
That nigger guitar player of yours,

01:31:05.882 --> 01:31:10.678
he didn't matter a shit. He was into
