01:31:11.137 --> 01:31:15.809
But this Krusemark dame, she comes
from a Louisiana money family.

01:31:16.267 --> 01:31:19.062
Two people bumped off in a week,
what's the connection?

01:31:19.521 --> 01:31:21.523
Similar circumstances!

01:31:21.981 --> 01:31:24.400
Did she have her dick cut off too?
- No!

01:31:24.859 --> 01:31:27.612
Some fucker cut her heart out,
neat as a butcher.

01:31:28.071 --> 01:31:31.324
Look, mine's
a missing persons, it's not a murder.

01:31:31.783 --> 01:31:36.287
I want the name of the party you're
looking for. - Talk to the lawyer.

01:31:36.746 --> 01:31:41.543
