Margaret wasn't evil.

01:38:34.044 --> 01:38:38.757
She was a strange kid! She was into
Tarot cards before she could read.

01:38:39.216 --> 01:38:42.886
Who got her started?
- Some maid, or governess, who knows.

01:38:43.345 --> 01:38:46.723
Everything you tell me
is a crock of shit!

01:38:47.182 --> 01:38:48.975
You got her started!

01:38:49.434 --> 01:38:54.272
You're a devil worshipper! - The Prince
of Darkness protects the powerful.

01:38:54.731 --> 01:38:56.733
Shit!
- I can't help if you don't believe it.

01:38:57.192 --> 01:39:01.279
Come straight with me, you slime-bag,
or I'll save the state an execution!

01:39:01.738 --> 01:39:04.783
I introduced
Johnny Favorite to my daughter.

01:39:05.242 --> 01:39:09.454
I watched him conjure up Lucifer in my
home. He was deeper in it than me.

01:39:09.913 --> 01:39:12.832
He made a pact with Satan.
He sold his soul.

01:39:13.291 --> 01:39:16.378
You expect me to swallow that?
- I don't give a damn!

01:39:16.836 --> 01:39:20.257
That's a crock of shit,
you lying toad!

01:39:20.715 --> 01:39:24.511
He sold his soul for stardom.
- For stardom?

01:39:24.970 --> 01:39:27.264
Satan rose from the depths.

01:39:27.722 --> 01:39:30.517
But he tried to outwit
the Prince of Darkness.

01:39:30.976 --> 01:39:34.229
When he made it big,
he tried to duck out of it.

01:39:34.688 --> 01:39:36.189
That's a crock of shit!

01:39:36.648 --> 01:39:40.485
Johnny found an obscure rite in an
ancient manuscript. He needed a victim.

01:39:40.944 --> 01:39:44.155
Someone his own age. - Why?
- To steal their soul.

01:39:44.614 --> 01:39:47.200
Toots and Johnny
picked up a young soldier.

01:39:47.659 --> 01:39:48.743
Who?
- Just a soldier

01:39:49.619 --> 01:39:51.121
celebrating New Year's Eve in New York.

01:39:52.497 --> 01:39:55.750
They took him back to Johnny's hotel,
where they had the ceremony.

01:39:56.209 --> 01:39:57.294
What ceremony?

01:39:57.752 --> 01:40:02.632
The boy was bound naked on a rubber mat,
there were complicated incantations.

01:40:03.091 --> 01:40:05.135
A pentacle was branded on his chest.

01:40:05.594 --> 01:40:07.262
Margaret gave Johnny a virgin dagger.

01:40:07.721 --> 01:40:10.765
He sliced the boy clean open
and ate his heart.

01:40:12.100 --> 01:40:15.312
It was still beating
when he wolfed it down.

01:40:16.980 --> 01:40:19.065
Johnny wanted to become that soldier.

01:40:19.524 --> 01:40:21.860
Before he had worked it out,
he was drafted,

01:40:22.319 --> 01:40:25.405
injured and sent home
without even knowing who he was.

01:40:25.864 --> 01:40:27.741
Who was the boy?

01:40:28.200 --> 01:40:32.996
Only Johnny knew. He put the dog tags
in a vase and gave it to Margaret.

01:40:33.455 --> 01:40:35.665
It was Margaret's plan
to drop him off in Times Square.

01:40:36.124 --> 01:40:38.877
The last place he remembered
before it happened.

01:40:43.340 --> 01:40:47.302
He needed a victim.
Someone his own age.

01:40:49.304 --> 01:40:52.098
To steal their soul.

01:40:52.933 --> 01:40:57.020
He sliced the boy clean open
and he ate his heart.

01:40:57.479 --> 01:40:59.397
Who was the boy?

01:41:00.607 --> 01:41:03.443
Johnny wanted to be the soldier.

01:41:05.278 --> 01:41:09.157
Maybe he gained the guy's soul,
but he still looked like Johnny to me.

01:43:31.716 --> 01:43:33.468
I know who I am!

01:43:54.281 --> 01:43:55.782
Alas...

01:43:58.869 --> 01:44:03.081
How terrible is wisdom if it brings
no profit to the wise, Johnny.

01:44:04.207 --> 01:44:06.001
Louis Cyphre...

01:44:08.295 --> 01:44:09.629
"Lucifer!"

01:44:12.007 --> 01:44:14.801
