01:44:50.837 --> 01:44:53.673
I know who I am.
You're trying to frame me.

01:44:54.424 --> 01:44:55.717
You're trying to frame me.

01:44:56.176 --> 01:45:00.722
I know who I am. You murdered them
people! I never killed nobody!

01:45:01.389 --> 01:45:03.725
I didn't kill Fowler,

01:45:06.144 --> 01:45:08.104
I didn't kill Toots,

01:45:08.563 --> 01:45:11.483
and I didn't kill Margaret or Krusemark.

01:45:11.942 --> 01:45:14.110
I killed no one.

01:45:14.569 --> 01:45:17.530
I'm afraid you did, Johnny.
- My name's not Johnny!

01:45:17.989 --> 01:45:22.369
All killed by your own hand.
Guided by me, naturally.

01:45:22.869 --> 01:45:27.499
You were doomed from the moment
you slit that young boy in half.

01:45:28.667 --> 01:45:33.505
You've been living on borrowed time and
another man's memories for 12 years.

01:45:37.884 --> 01:45:42.138
I want to tell Winesap, he knows!
- He's dead.

01:45:43.348 --> 01:45:44.391
Nasty accident!

01:45:46.601 --> 01:45:51.815
Don't worry, no one will mourn one less
lawyer. Death's everywhere these days.

01:45:54.234 --> 01:45:57.988
But what gives
human life its worth, anyway?

01:45:58.738 --> 01:46:01.658
Because someone loves it, hates it.

01:46:02.117 --> 01:46:06.288
The flesh is weak.
Only the soul is immortal.

01:46:11.918 --> 01:46:14.546
And yours belongs to me!

01:46:19.467 --> 01:46:21.261
I know who I am.

01:46:25.348 --> 01:46:28.602
That's it Johnny, take a good look!

01:46:29.644 --> 01:46:32.856
However cleverly you
sneak up on the mirror, your reflection

01:46:33.315 --> 01:46:37.110
always looks you straight in the eye.
- I know who I am.

01:47:07.891 --> 01:47:09.893
I know who I am!

01:48:22.257 --> 01:48:23.884
Why did you come back?

01:48:34.227 --> 01:48:36.104
I live here.

01:48:37.772 --> 01:48:39.316
Who is she?

01:48:41.735 --> 01:48:45.071
